channel.title: How do i remove an item?
channel.description:
I want to remove an item from my server, the Dharoks Helm because when u wear full dharoks you hit like 60s and 70s.
I went to Item.cfg and removed it and compiled but i can still spawn it and its still in the shops.

item.title: How do i remove an item?
item.dc:creator: @runegay runegay
item.description:
@runegay wrote:

u probably shouldnt because it would mess up the server, just edit the item bonuses:

item = 4716	Dharoks_helm	Dharok_the_Wretched's_helm.	63377.3753241266	63377.3753241266	83312.2081494279	(0	0	0	-3	-1	45	48	44	-1	51	5	0)

the numbers in the parantheses are the stats u can edit, the big numbers before them are item buyin/selling/alching
